ENTRY            40841   20251006   20260319   20260319       4226
SUBENT        40841001   20251006   20260319   20260319       4226
BIB                 12         50
TITLE        Absolute measurements of fission cross-sections
           of 234U, 236U, 240Pu, 241Pu1 and 243Am by the neutrons
           of CF-252 fission spectrum
AUTHOR     (V.M.Adamov,S.E.Gusev,L.V.Drapchinskiy,V.V.Kol'tsov,
           S.S.Kovalenko,O.I.Kostochkin,K.A.Petrzhak,
           L.A.Pleskachevskiy,A.M.Sokolov,S.M.Solov'ev,
           P.S.Soloshenkov,V.A.Trenkin)
REFERENCE  ((S,INDC(CCP)-235,(2),134,1984)=
           (C,83KIEV,2,134,1983)) Vol. II
INSTITUTE  (4RUSRI)
INC-SOURCE (CF252)
INC-SPECT    Cf-252 fission spectrum
METHOD     (ASSOP)  Combined method of coincidence and
           (COINC)  associated particles
MONITOR     No information.
ASSUMED    (ASSUM,98-CF-252(N,F),PR,NU) From ENDF-B/V.
REL-REF    (R,,V.M.Surin+,J,YK,,(4/48),3,1982) Reference for
                                                half-lives.
           (M,,V.M.Adamov+,C,75KIEV,6,19,1975) =
           (M,,V.M.Adamov+,S,INDC(CCP)-099,(4),19,1976)
            Experim.details
           (M,,V.M.Adamov+,C,79KNOX,,995,1979)   Experim.det.
ERR-ANALYS (ERR-1) Error due to the NU-BAR of Cf-252 .
           (ERR-2) Error due to the geometrical factor .
           (ERR-3) Error caused by the solid angle .
           (ERR-4) Error due to the layer mass determination
                   statistics .
           (ERR-5) Error due to the half-life uncertainty .
           (ERR-6) Error due to the spectrum extrapolation
                   to zero energy .
           (ERR-7) Error due to the layer absorption .
           (ERR-S) Error due to the coincidence statistic
           (ERR-T) Total Error.
HISTORY    (19850115C)
           (20090417U) M.M. BIB information was added.
            Free text was corrected to be human-readable.
            Dates were corrected for 4-digits year.
            ASSUM and ASSUM-ERR units were corrected:
             NO-DIM -> PRT/FIS .
           (20160603A) SD: DECAY-DATA corrected in Subent 005.
           Refs C,75KIEV,6,19,1975; C,79KNOX,,995,1979 moved to
           REL-REF.
           (20170710U) M.M. Previous correction of SD was
           checked at CJD.
           J,YK,1982,(4/48),3,1982 -> J,YK,,(4/48),3,1982 -REL-REF
           Two refs. INDC(CCP)- reps. were added .
           EN-DUMMY=1.5 MeV -> KT-DUMMY=1.42 MeV according to
           a comment of N.Otsuka (NDS,IAEA) .
           (20251006A) Ref. S,INDC(CCP)-235 was corrected.
           STATUS was corrected for new rules.
ENDBIB              50
COMMON               6          3
KT-DUMMY   ASSUM      ASSUM-ERR  ERR-1      ERR-2      ERR-3
MEV        PRT/FIS    PRT/FIS    PER-CENT   PER-CENT   PER-CENT
 1.42       3.758      0.009      0.2        0.58       0.20
ENDCOMMON            3
ENDSUBENT           57
SUBENT        40841002   20251006   20260319   20260319       4226
BIB                  3          6
REACTION   (92-U-234(N,F),,SIG,,FIS)
ANALYSIS    Half-life of 92-U-234 alpha-decay 2.445E+5 +-0.010E+5
            years was used to define the number of nucleus in
            sample.
STATUS     (TABLE,,V.M.Adamov+,S,INDC(CCP)-235,(2),134,1984)
            Table 1
ENDBIB               6
